{"tid":1887028,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"富臨20間餐館短暫休業　2千名員工放3天無薪假期","createTime":"2020-02-19T09:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T11:06:20.000Z","uid":152476,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0e546d5c706c5c6db2221668dee65ac87fbe1bc0","tid":1887028,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n富臨集團宣布，因應新型肺炎疫情令市民減少外出用膳，管理層在審慎考慮後，決定旗下約20間餐館短暫休業，進行徹底清潔和消毒。<br />\n<br />\n而因應營業店舖減少，前線員工本月需按既定程序，安排放3天無薪假期，受影響員工約2000名，但強調現時未有裁員計劃。<br />\n<br />\n另外，公司指，疫情進一步打擊零售餐飲市道，集團跟大部部業主磋商租金紓緩措施，並推行一系列營運成本控制方案，包括本月內下調全體執行董事薪酬50%、下調高級管理層薪酬20%，作為降低成本的第一步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509498-20200219.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509498-20200219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5N4xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=f3523408\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509498-20200219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9d93fd97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509498-20200219.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"30bc0b8b075e51375b93a29e0f699a2601ba7cee","tid":1887028,"uid":188133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"休休下會唔會成間消失埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438c00a63229bdcaa541ea0a0cb74b748d6dac2f","tid":1887028,"uid":283189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:38:08.000Z","msg":"福建幫全家死清光<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d544660753f4361f69dedea13412b4897fc56d3e","tid":1887028,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"